  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The investigators hypothesize that non-optimally treated carbohydrate counting-naïve patients
      with type 1 diabetes can achieve better metabolic control by counting carbohydrates and that
      the metabolic control can be further improved with concurrent use of an integrated glucose
      meter and bolus calculator. The investigators want to test the hypothesis in this study.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
